Steps.Message: Update at 09:49 - We're very sorry we've had to switch off your electricity today. If you were not proactively contacted shortly after the power went off, please call us on 08003163105 and we can update the contact information we've received from your energy supplier. With this, we can ensure we proactively contact you in case of any future power cuts, except overnight.

We became aware of this power cut at 08:17. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
Steps.Name: We are restoring customers automatically
